         <abstract id="aspace_dd19ebbc44fcd4fdb1755349146771eb">The records consist of correspondence, recommendations, letters, newspaper clippings, printed materials, applications, and nominations documenting the 1978 search committee for a dean of the Yale School of Drama.</abstract>
